ent-CMMagazinePistolM77AP = Mod 88 AP magazine (9mm)
    .desc = A 19-round armor-piercing magazine for the Mod 88 combat pistol. It has found common use with We-Yu PMC operators to defeat armored threats when terminal effect is authorized.

ent-CMMagazinePistolM88Rubber = Mod 88 rubber magazine (9mm)
    .desc = A 19-round rubber magazine for the Mod 88 combat pistol. The blue stripe and safety markings designate the non-lethal load designed to deform and deliver blunt-force trauma on impact. Standard issue to leverage security and suppression without creating unnecessary casualties.

ent-RMCWeaponPistolM77 = Mod 88 combat pistol
    .desc = Standard issue Marine firearm. Also found in the hands of We-Yu PMC teams. Fires 9mm armor shredding rounds and is capable of 3-round burst.

